SSH Connection Manager




_______________________


Features:

- add ips
- add notes / port / hostname / custom params to connection
- modify your entry
- list all your entries
- connect
- change behavior in config file (delete obsolete or old connections)
- sort them by frequency
- allow different settings for a connection (nesting)
- set alias for favourite connection -> quickconnect 
- search
- connect to all ips in range 192.168.0.1..190 found..
- connect to all ips with 'admin' in notes



